[I] A fast and powerful twin-panel file manager for the Linux desktop.

[T] GNOME Commander is a "two-pane" graphical filemanager for the Gnome desktop
[T] environment. GNOME Commander aims to fulfill the demands of more advanced
[T] users who like to focus on file management, their work through special
[T] applications and running smart commands.

[U] https://gnome.pages.gitlab.gnome.org/gnome-commander/

